review: We had not been to this location in a while, and now I remember why.  In a word, SLOW!!!  Both service and kitchen staff here take forever - we waited over twenty minutes just for our drinks (non-alcoholic) to be brought to us.  Our food took another fourty minutes after that, even though we had placed our order at the same time we gave the server our drink orders.  Won't be visiting this location any time in the near future (if ever again)!
